    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved Level 1 vs. required Level 2) is acknowledged; the limitation is considered acceptable given that ASTM F1717 prescribes a single standard test configuration and the validation QoIs satisfy all quantitative acceptance criteria. Overall credibility is assessed as sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
